      "text": [
        " ثَوْبِ اَلْإِحْرَامِ فَقَالَ «لاَ بَأْسَ بِهِمَا هُمَا طَهُورَانِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2612 - Hammad ibn Uthman asked Abu Abdullah (as) about the khaluq of the Ka'bah and the khaluq of the grave that might be present on the Ihram garment.\nImam (as) said: \"There is no harm in them; both are pure.\""
        ]
      }
